name: 01. PRIDE
description: I don´t care about your previous life, if it hurts your already know, words lie in deceive, over time, covered lies, become allies with your steps. On the fire, burns the skin of your charm, far is now the memory, like a light glimpse of 6 years, eternally dying inside, living forever in cosmos. The fear of a change and the wait tend to be rough. The everlasting moments when you come back from so far away, when you arrive, whenever you want, your words and mine.
